headline: Why Moderna (MRNA) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of biotechnology company Moderna (NASDAQ:MRNA) jumped 3.6% in the afternoon session after the company announced it received U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) approval for its updated COVID-19 vaccines for the 2025-2026 season.
